Implement TPU-optimized kernels for Flash Attention, GEMM, and Layer Normalization
- Added TPUFlashAttention class for efficient Flash Attention computation with O(1) memory complexity. - Introduced TPUGEMMKernel for optimized General Matrix Multiplication with support for mixed precision and tiling. - Created TPULayerNormKernel for layer normalization with options for bias, scaling, and fused operations. - Each kernel includes forward and backward pass methods, ensuring compatibility with TPU hardware. - Implemented dynamic padding and layout optimization for improved performance on TPU.
